text: The Cadillac Celestiq is an all-electric luxury sedan made by Cadillac It was revealed in 2021 and started production in 2024. The Celestiq is Cadillac`s new flagship car and the sucessor of The Cadillac CT6 its part of the General Motors eletrification strategy. == References == Celestiq Category:2020s automobiles Category:Sedans
